{"tid":825290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（先達狗 聲大大屈人）","createTime":"2018-09-17T12:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T14:34:53.000Z","uid":209790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"210ba2d2cb149f8095c0416a4d3ef0ec6613a9b3","tid":825290,"uid":209790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"因為本人有野做緊 所以叫左我fd幫我去先達放部三星S9+ 部機 我部機果時 唔記得講個密碼佢知 鎖密碼原因係驚收機佬 會搞其他資料。<br />\n<br />\n之後個先達狗check完機 就話我個fd部機（姐係我部機）有人報失，之後我fd打比我 我就趕過黎解鎖比個先達佬睇啦 點知條先達佬唔比部機我解鎖 仲要收埋我部機 。仲要兇鳩我地 之後話報警 之後我咪話報警啦 部機係我嘅 點會係報失機阿 你老母擺明想呃鳩我地呢啲人啦 <br />\n<br />\n單純就好呃啲ga？當我地係傻仔？<br />\n<br />\n中途仲有啲隔離舖頭嘅人 過黎兇鳩我啲 個語氣真係好撚臭串 語氣似問候你老母果啲啦<br />\n<br />\n最後警察黎左 佢叫我解鎖 我解完比個差佬睇 條收機佬先肯死死氣比返部機我 <br />\n<br />\n如果佢地講野唔甘串都無乜嘢啊 屈完我地仲要聲大大甘撚樣！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/205226_015f8b4982bf0e83cf7839f188982980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F205226_015f8b4982bf0e83cf7839f188982980.png&h=7693e556&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/205228_e7d26983f9d9b08a4d85a2ed2d09f6f9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F205228_e7d26983f9d9b08a4d85a2ed2d09f6f9.png&h=c59ba904&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/205230_079ef92a273ff5ac4a81c674bc57f58b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F205230_079ef92a273ff5ac4a81c674bc57f58b.png&h=0fe87eb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f502ea38b3ca4dc448a8708c6da17af2e1ee12e2","tid":825290,"uid":49669,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先達唔喺普通人入去的"},{"pid":"c4ab95430ad78ada37994d518748d5953b074fb6","tid":825290,"uid":1834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"